" Coq is case sensitive.
syn case match

syn cluster coqVernac contains=coqRequire,coqCheck,coqEval,coqNotation,coqTacNotation,coqDecl,coqThm,coqLtacDecl,coqDef,coqFix,coqInd,coqRec,coqShow

