   " Comments
   HiLink coqComment                   Comment
   HiLink coqProofComment coqComment

   " Todo
   HiLink coqTodo                      Todo

   " Errors
   HiLink coqError                     Error

   " Strings
   HiLink coqString                    String

 delcommand HiLink
endif

